      • compareBuren

        public boolean compareBuren(Node n)
        Compares the neighbors of two nodes by degree. If a node's neighbors' degree sequence is identical to this node's, then their neighbors are considered equal.
        Parameters:
        n - The node to be compared to this one.
        Returns:
        true if the neighbors of node n have the same degrees as this node's neighbors.
